custom: jq '.version = "1.0.6"' package.json > tmp.json && mv tmp.json package.json

jebbs.plantuml.prepublish: wget -O plantuml.zip https://sourceforge.net/projects/plantuml/files/1.2021.0/plantuml-jar-mit-1.2021.0.zip/download && unzip plantuml.zip && rm plantuml.zip && mv COPYING COPYING.plantuml-jar

llam4u.nerdtree.prepublish: sed /\.svg/d README.md > README.md.tmp && mv README.md.tmp README.md

ms-pyright.vscode-pyright.prepublish: npm i && cd packages/vscode-pyright && npm run prepackage

custom: python -m pip install nox flake8 autopep8

ms-python.debugpy.prepublish: python -m pip install -U pip pipx wheel && npm ci --prefer-offline && python -m pipx run nox --session install_bundled_libs

custom: python -m pip install --no-user --no-deps --require-hashes --only-binary :all: -t ./python_files/lib/jedilsp --implementation py --platform any --abi none -r ./python_files/jedilsp_requirements/requirements.txt
npm ci --ignore-scripts --prefer-offline --no-audit && npm run postinstall && npm run package

ms-vscode.js-debug.prepublish: npm run compile && npm run package

custom: cd wasm-wasi-core && jq '.scripts["update:version"] = ""' package.json > tmp.json && mv tmp.json package.json
npm i && cd wasm-wasi-core && vsce package -o extension.vsix
npm i && cd webshell && vsce package -o extension.vsix
echo 'apt-get install -y apt-transport-https dirmngr gnupg ca-certificates' >> /tmp/build-godot.sh
echo 'su -c "npx --package vsce vsce package -o extension.vsix" node' >> /tmp/build-godot.sh
[ $MS_VERSION = '1.0.0' ] && npm remove --save-dev vscode && npm install --save-dev typescript@3 @types/vscode@1.23 @types/node@7 || true
[ $VERSION = '1.2.4' ] && npx haxelib install vscode && npx haxelib install vscode-debugadapter || true
